cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "open_research_skill"
type: software
description: >-
  A multi-source open-access research skill for autonomous AI agents.
  Integrates OpenAlex, arXiv, CrossRef, Semantic Scholar, and PubMed Central
  with a four-tier citation provenance system that prevents hallucinated
  references by requiring each citation to be grounded in actual document content.
