version: "1.0.0"
release-date: "2026-05-12"
abstract: >-
  open_research_skill is a modular research tool for AI agents that automates
  literature search, paper retrieval, full-text reading, and citation management
  across five open-access academic sources. Its key innovation is a four-tier
  citation provenance system that prevents hallucinated references by requiring
  each citation to be grounded in actual document content, with verification
  tiers ranging from full PDF parsing with page-level references to metadata-only
  discovery.
